00:31:38.920 --> 00:31:46.600
All the French paid for these facilities — at least those who had a car, everytime they stopped at a tollbooth!

00:31:47.120 --> 00:31:54.080
I know there's an ecological criticism that consists n saying that the more highways, the more cars,

00:31:54.320 --> 00:31:58.540
and of course, the more cars, the more pollution.

00:31:58.700 --> 00:32:04.300
And above all, the more cars, the more we need highways, and so on.

00:32:04.340 --> 00:32:09.440
So we clearly see that this is a vicious circle,
but for now, we still have these highway companies,

00:32:09.440 --> 00:32:15.220
and everyday, people keep paying for the profits of these companies when they stop at a tollbooth

00:32:15.600 --> 00:32:23.120
To me, when the time comes, our majority MPs will have to create a parliamentary commission of inquiry

00:32:23.500 --> 00:32:27.380
in order to shed light on the reasons why and the conditions in which highways were sold,

00:32:27.820 --> 00:32:29.680
and on the problems caused by this sale.

00:32:29.860 --> 00:32:36.440
There are lots of politicians that say that this privatization was a scandal.

00:32:36.680 --> 00:32:42.260
Highway companies raised toll rates but they didn't make any additional investment.

00:32:42.720 --> 00:32:47.580
Highway companies are like other companies — and some of them were very straightforward!

00:32:47.800 --> 00:32:51.100
They said they would put money for five years in order to pay off their investment,

00:32:51.320 --> 00:32:56.220
in other words, to yield the highest returns they could get, but they did not intend to make investments at all.

00:32:56.220 --> 00:33:00.240
This is why I intend to nationalize highways,

00:33:00.620 --> 00:33:02.980
because highways were everyone's property,

00:33:03.320 --> 00:33:10.500
and to me, they were sold at an absurdly cheap price.

00:33:10.980 --> 00:33:16.260
It's not possible to assess the price of something at a given moment

00:33:16.480 --> 00:33:20.180
when it is supposed to function for 20 or 30 years.
This is an illusion.

00:33:20.180 --> 00:33:22.300
The market price my foot!

00:33:22.540 --> 00:33:24.980
